{"tid":1498774,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"死蝗仔，縮番入去你老母個閪度啦","createTime":"2019-08-23T13:39:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T13:51:50.000Z","uid":142358,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6a5de1167725cebd30b8688fc562d3298afd8058","tid":1498774,"uid":142358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:39:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隻死肥閪向手足們舉完中指，又係咁向手足做挑釁手勢，又喺度屌班手足<br />\n雖然個死靚仔講講廣東話，但係都遮唔到陣蝗味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n後面嗰個係佢老母，本來想屌佢老母，知道後面嗰個係佢老母之後，都係不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我想話，香港人真係幾克制，尤其是我隔離嗰位手足哥哥，啱啱屌完隻蝗，跟住就有阿嬸問佢路，聽到蝗語，手足哥哥即刻好有禮貌咁話<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你用廣東話我咪答你囉</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後阿嬸即刻敗走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於呢件事我只有一個感想，就係<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"021859dfb34620bb3bf7020a66d8c54eac0a6d56","tid":1498774,"uid":227174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:41:23.000Z","msg":"邊間學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"566ed952773128961312f7dc8161268034dd9990","tid":1498774,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:42:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6da7072253cc4a55254e9f6c930a28acd6d8d07b","tid":1498774,"uid":142358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"021859dfb34620bb3bf7020a66d8c54eac0a6d56","tid":1498774,"uid":227174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:41:23.000Z","msg":"邊間學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:43:49.000Z","msg":"就係想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" cl